00:12:28.850 --> 00:12:32.420 align:middle line:10%
and every single human
being is a messenger.

00:12:32.420 --> 00:12:36.198 align:middle line:84%
So I don't want to give anyone
the impression that I imagine

00:12:36.198 --> 00:12:38.240 align:middle line:84%
or that I would even allow
anyone else to imagine

00:12:38.240 --> 00:12:40.430 align:middle line:84%
that I'm somehow
separate from or

00:12:40.430 --> 00:12:42.618 align:middle line:90%
other than the average person.

00:12:42.618 --> 00:12:44.910 align:middle line:84%
>> That would be part of
those illusions, would it not?

00:12:44.910 --> 00:12:45.785 align:middle line:90%
>> It would, in fact.

00:12:45.785 --> 00:12:48.950 align:middle line:84%
>> Exactly, only you have
brought it to a point--

00:12:48.950 --> 00:12:51.290 align:middle line:84%
and as I said, I think
it's in 25 languages

00:12:51.290 --> 00:12:53.960 align:middle line:84%
and millions of copies have
