he was dealing with from sex

00:13:00.996 --> 00:13:01.170 align:middle line:90%
and relationships.

00:13:01.170 --> 00:13:02.840 align:middle line:84%
>> Of course, I didn't
do it-- yes, that's true,

00:13:02.840 --> 00:13:04.257 align:middle line:84%
but I didn't do
that deliberately.

00:13:04.257 --> 00:13:07.580 align:middle line:84%
I mean, there was no
thought about it in my head.

00:13:07.580 --> 00:13:10.792 align:middle line:84%
I think God has had a
plan, but I had none.

00:13:10.792 --> 00:13:13.000 align:middle line:84%
Really, the first book wasn't
even written as a book.

00:13:13.000 --> 00:13:17.780 align:middle line:84%
It was simply a bunch of
pages in my personal journal.

00:13:17.780 --> 00:13:20.390 align:middle line:84%
And I got a legal
pad, actually, and I

00:13:20.390 --> 00:13:22.100 align:middle line:84%
was writing to
myself for myself,

00:13:22.100 --> 00:13:25.160 align:middle line:84%
never even imagining that
anyone would ever see it.

00:13:25.160 --> 00:13:26.850 align:middle line:84%
So it wasn't as if
I sat down and said,

00:13:26.850 --> 00:13:28.852 align:middle line:84%
OK, the first book
will be at this level,

00:13:28.852 --> 00:13:31.310 align:middle line:84%
the second book at this level,
and the third, and so forth.

00:13:31.310 --> 00:13:33.260 align:middle line:84%
What happened, however,
as an organic part

00:13:33.260 --> 00:13:37.040 align:middle line:84%
of the process that was going
on in my life, the material

00:13:37.040 --> 00:13:40.670 align:middle line:84%
from Book 1 to Book 5
in the "With God" series

00:13:40.670 --> 00:13:44.930 align:middle line:84%
began to increase in complexity
and in spiritual sophistication

00:13:44.930 --> 00:13:46.880 align:middle line:84%
until now, with
"Communion With God,"

00:13:46.880 --> 00:13:48.800 align:middle line:84%
we have a highly
sophisticated piece

00:13:48.800 --> 00:13:50.900 align:middle line:84%
of spiritual material
that explains

00:13:50.900 --> 00:13:54.620 align:middle line:84%
the cosmological
construction of our life.

00:13:54.620 --> 00:13:57.560 align:middle line:84%
>> And it does, as I said,
talk about the God within,

00:13:57.560 --> 00:13:59.510 align:middle line:84%
that we are God,
we are the creator.

00:13:59.510 --> 00:14:04.280 align:middle line:84%
It empowers us in a
way that would allow

00:14:04.280 --> 00:14:06.475 align:middle line:90%
us to master the illusions.

00:14:06.475 --> 00:14:07.850 align:middle line:84%
And there's one
of those sections

00:14:07.850 --> 00:14:09.430 align:middle line:84%
that you have on
mastering the illusions.

00:14:09.430 --> 00:14:11.305 align:middle line:84%
>> That's the beauty of
"Communion With God."

00:14:11.305 --> 00:14:13.980 align:middle line:84%
It not only lists the 10
illusions of human beings,

00:14:13.980 --> 00:14:16.100 align:middle line:84%
but it lists, one chapter
for each illusion,

00:14:16.100 --> 00:14:18.680 align:middle line:84%
how to step outside
of those illusions

00:14:18.680 --> 00:14:20.630 align:middle line:84%
and live with them
but not within them

00:14:20.630 --> 00:14:23.540 align:middle line:84%
or, as some prior teachers have
said, how to be in this world

00:14:23.540 --> 00:14:24.530 align:middle line:90%
but not of it.

00:14:24.530 --> 00:14:28.070 align:middle line:84%
And then the book concludes
with some wonderful text

00:14:28.070 --> 00:14:31.340 align:middle line:84%
dealing with the experience
of meeting with the creator

00:14:31.340 --> 00:14:34.437 align:middle line:84%
and having an actual communion
with God in one's own life.

00:14:34.437 --> 00:14:36.020 align:middle line:84%
So I think it's an
extraordinary book.

00:14:36.020 --> 00:14:38.930 align:middle line:84%
I'm very, very excited about
it and just very humbled

00:14:38.930 --> 00:14:41.330 align:middle line:84%
to have been able to play a
part in bringing it through.

00:14:41.330 --> 00:14:44.120 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, and as you move through
those illusions and then you

00:14:44.120 --> 00:14:47.570 align:middle line:84%
teach us how we can master them
or how the information is being

00:14:47.570 --> 00:14:51.380 align:middle line:84%
shared, each of us then in our
own lives can have that kind

00:14:51.380 --> 00:14:53.210 align:middle line:90%
of identification, as I said.

00:14:53.210 --> 00:14:55.370 align:middle line:84%
How have I practiced
that illusion?

00:14:55.370 --> 00:14:56.902 align:middle line:90%
How can I-- and do you know--

00:14:56.902 --> 00:14:58.610 align:middle line:84%
it's interesting
because it serves people

00:14:58.610 --> 00:15:02.180 align:middle line:84%
very well when you can bring
it then to the practical level

00:15:02.180 --> 00:15:05.720 align:middle line:84%
again and realize that in
a situation when you are

00:15:05.720 --> 00:15:07.970 align:middle line:90%
very upset, you should not be.

00:15:07.970 --> 00:15:09.380 align:middle line:84%
That's when you
step back from it

00:15:09.380 --> 00:15:11.730 align:middle line:84%
and you kind of practice
these principles.

00:15:11.730 --> 00:15:11.810 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:15:11.810 --> 00:15:13.435 align:middle line:84%
I'm not sure I would
say you should not

00:15:13.435 --> 00:15:15.240 align:middle line:84%
be because there are
no shoulds in life,

00:15:15.240 --> 00:15:17.465 align:middle line:84%
and I always tell people,
"Don't should on yourself."

00:15:17.465 --> 00:15:19.632 align:middle line:84%
So I'm not sure that I would
say that you should not

00:15:19.632 --> 00:15:20.608 align:middle line:90%
be very upset.

00:15:20.608 --> 00:15:23.150 align:middle line:84%
I think what I would say is you
have a choice not to be upset

00:15:23.150 --> 00:15:24.983 align:middle line:84%
and you will be upset
or not upset depending

00:15:24.983 --> 00:15:27.050 align:middle line:84%
on what you assess
is of greatest

00:15:27.050 --> 00:15:29.960 align:middle line:84%
benefit to you and to
the world that you touch

00:15:29.960 --> 00:15:32.240 align:middle line:84%
and to the experience
you're creating.

00:15:32.240 --> 00:15:34.430 align:middle line:84%
Less and less in my life
do I experience that it's

00:15:34.430 --> 00:15:36.200 align:middle line:90%
beneficial for me to be upset.

00:15:36.200 --> 00:15:39.200 align:middle line:84%
And sometimes I do get upset and
I demonstrate my upsetedness,

00:15:39.200 --> 00:15:42.200 align:middle line:84%
but fewer times now than, let's
say, three or four or five

00:15:42.200 --> 00:15:45.430 align:middle line:84%
years ago and far fewer
than 10 or 20 years ago.

00:15:45.430 --> 00:15:47.413 align:middle line:84%
So I'm really a changed
man in that regard.

00:15:47.413 --> 00:15:48.830 align:middle line:84%
And I still have
a long way to go.

00:15:48.830 --> 00:15:50.710 align:middle line:90%
>> While you are evolving--

00:15:50.710 --> 00:15:53.120 align:middle line:84%
that's part of the job of us
being here on the planet is

00:15:53.120 --> 00:15:54.868 align:middle line:90%
to evolve, to move closer to.

00:15:54.868 --> 00:15:55.910 align:middle line:90%
>> It's what we're up to.

00:15:55.910 --> 00:15:56.870 align:middle line:90%
It's the whole process.

00:15:56.870 --> 00:15:59.000 align:middle line:84%
The process of life
itself is the process

00:15:59.000 --> 00:16:01.940 align:middle line:84%
by which human beings and
all species in the universe

00:16:01.940 --> 00:16:05.360 align:middle line:84%
evolve to higher and
higher expressions of who

00:16:05.360 --> 00:16:06.830 align:middle line:90%
we all really are.

00:16:06.830 --> 00:16:09.410 align:middle line:84%
In a sense, we are
God godding or God

00:16:09.410 --> 00:16:11.630 align:middle line:84%
becoming the next
grandest version of who

00:16:11.630 --> 00:16:14.150 align:middle line:90%
God imagines God's self to be.

00:16:14.150 --> 00:16:16.705 align:middle line:84%
>> Now a lot of people-- the
controversy might come with

00:16:16.705 --> 00:16:19.730 align:middle line:84%
the people who don't think
of themselves as God.

00:16:19.730 --> 00:16:22.520 align:middle line:84%
And with that,
how do you explain

00:16:22.520 --> 00:16:24.830 align:middle line:84%
that we aren't really
separate from God, there's

00:16:24.830 --> 00:16:27.570 align:middle line:90%
that illusion of separation?

00:16:27.570 --> 00:16:30.230 align:middle line:84%
>> I don't know how
anyone else explains it.

00:16:30.230 --> 00:16:33.430 align:middle line:84%
What I say is what I was
given in the material.

00:16:33.430 --> 00:16:34.430 align:middle line:90%
There is only one thing.

00:16:34.430 --> 00:16:36.070 align:middle line:84%
In the beginning, all
there was is all there is,

00:16:36.070 --> 00:16:37.550 align:middle line:84%
and all there is
is all there was,

00:16:37.550 --> 00:16:39.080 align:middle line:90%
and there was nothing else.

00:16:39.080 --> 00:16:40.970 align:middle line:84%
Now most people agree
to that when you say,

00:16:40.970 --> 00:16:43.040 align:middle line:84%
"In the beginning, all
there is all there was,

00:16:43.040 --> 00:16:44.267 align:middle line:90%
and there was nothing else."

00:16:44.267 --> 00:16:46.850 align:middle line:84%
Most people can say, "Yes, we've
kind of been taught something

00:16:46.850 --> 00:16:48.860 align:middle line:90%
like that in our own childhood."

00:16:48.860 --> 00:16:51.950 align:middle line:84%
But then I say, "OK, just
do not accept the mythology

00:16:51.950 --> 00:16:54.650 align:middle line:84%
that somehow between
the beginning and now,

00:16:54.650 --> 00:16:58.400 align:middle line:84%
we were separated off from
all that is, that we somehow

00:16:58.400 --> 00:17:02.090 align:middle line:84%
got separated, leaving all
that is over there as God

00:17:02.090 --> 00:17:03.710 align:middle line:84%
and leaving us over
here as somehow

00:17:03.710 --> 00:17:05.089 align:middle line:90%
other than all that is."

00:17:05.089 --> 00:17:08.419 align:middle line:84%
If God is truly all that
is, all that ever was

00:17:08.419 --> 00:17:10.609 align:middle line:84%
and all that ever will
be, world without end,

00:17:10.609 --> 00:17:13.520 align:middle line:84%
that would have to
include us by definition.

00:17:13.520 --> 00:17:16.160 align:middle line:84%
And if it includes
us by definition,

00:17:16.160 --> 00:17:20.599 align:middle line:84%
then to deny that we are an
aspect or a part of that which

00:17:20.599 --> 00:17:26.020 align:middle line:84%
we call God or life itself would
be to deny our very existence.

00:17:26.020 --> 00:17:27.130 align:middle line:90%
>> The oneness.

00:17:27.130 --> 00:17:29.080 align:middle line:84%
You have statements
of ultimate truth,

00:17:29.080 --> 00:17:32.440 align:middle line:84%
and this is what we are
supposed to remind ourselves.

00:17:32.440 --> 00:17:34.780 align:middle line:90%
"Nothing in my world is real.

00:17:34.780 --> 00:17:38.050 align:middle line:84%
The meaning of everything
is the meaning I give it.

00:17:38.050 --> 00:17:41.050 align:middle line:84%
I am who I say I am
and my experience

00:17:41.050 --> 00:17:42.400 align:middle line:90%
is that what I say it is."

00:17:42.400 --> 00:17:44.480 align:middle line:84%
>> My experience is
what I say it is, yes.

00:17:44.480 --> 00:17:45.280 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:17:45.280 --> 00:17:47.800 align:middle line:84%
>> Those are three incredibly
powerful statements that can

00:17:47.800 --> 00:17:50.470 align:middle line:84%
change one's life
virtually overnight.

00:17:50.470 --> 00:17:54.370 align:middle line:84%
>> And so in each
situation, if we go to that,

00:17:54.370 --> 00:17:55.940 align:middle line:90%
we remember our ultimate truths.

00:17:55.940 --> 00:17:57.550 align:middle line:90%
And you also have the triad.

00:17:57.550 --> 00:17:59.950 align:middle line:84%
And this is, "See the
illusion as an illusion,

00:17:59.950 --> 00:18:03.280 align:middle line:84%
decide what it means, and
recreate yourself anew."

00:18:03.280 --> 00:18:06.310 align:middle line:84%
>> This is the process by which
we work with the illusions

00:18:06.310 --> 00:18:08.480 align:middle line:84%
and change our moment
to moment experience.

00:18:08.480 --> 00:18:09.280 align:middle line:90%
>> OK.

00:18:09.280 --> 00:18:11.530 align:middle line:84%
>> See the illusion as an
illusion and decide what you

00:18:11.530 --> 00:18:12.440 align:middle line:90%
want it to mean.

00:18:12.440 --> 00:18:12.730 align:middle line:90%
>> OK.

00:18:12.730 --> 00:18:15.220 align:middle line:84%
So that's when we have to
go into that witness state

00:18:15.220 --> 00:18:17.230 align:middle line:90%
and step back in each situation?

00:18:17.230 --> 00:18:18.042 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes, exactly.

00:18:18.042 --> 00:18:20.500 align:middle line:84%
It's a wonderful way you've
put it, to go into that witness

00:18:20.500 --> 00:18:22.780 align:middle line:84%
state, to witness
our own experience

00:18:22.780 --> 00:18:24.880 align:middle line:84%
and then call it what
you choose to call it,

00:18:24.880 --> 00:18:26.830 align:middle line:84%
knowing that it
really all is illusory

00:18:26.830 --> 00:18:29.100 align:middle line:84%
and you can call it whatever
you wish to call it.

00:18:29.100 --> 00:18:31.180 align:middle line:10%
