was one of those--

00:18:31.180 --> 00:18:34.630 align:middle line:10%
would be in a very bad situation
and say, "This is a blessing.

00:18:34.630 --> 00:18:36.880 align:middle line:10%
And I may not be able to
experience the blessing right

00:18:36.880 --> 00:18:39.070 align:middle line:10%
now, but I know that
before too much time

00:18:39.070 --> 00:18:42.472 align:middle line:10%
goes by I will see the blessing
that God has given me here."

00:18:42.472 --> 00:18:43.930 align:middle line:84%
And I would say to
her, "How do you

00:18:43.930 --> 00:18:45.805 align:middle line:84%
know that God has given
you a blessing here?"

00:18:45.805 --> 00:18:47.380 align:middle line:84%
And my mother would
say, "Because God

00:18:47.380 --> 00:18:50.620 align:middle line:84%
gives me nothing else
but blessings ever."

00:18:50.620 --> 00:18:51.770 align:middle line:10%
>> And from experience--

00:18:51.770 --> 00:18:53.560 align:middle line:10%
>> She was a woman of
great, great faith.

00:18:53.560 --> 00:18:56.710 align:middle line:84%
>> She probably from her
experiences then had seen how

00:18:56.710 --> 00:18:58.330 align:middle line:84%
that had been true
and how that had--

00:18:58.330 --> 00:18:58.550 align:middle line:90%
>> In her life.

00:18:58.550 --> 00:18:59.610 align:middle line:90%
>> --worked out in her life.

00:18:59.610 --> 00:19:00.410 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:19:00.410 --> 00:19:04.000 align:middle line:10%
>> And we can too if we reflect
back and see those things that

00:19:04.000 --> 00:19:06.560 align:middle line:10%
we thought were wrong and
what happened as a result,

00:19:06.560 --> 00:19:08.485 align:middle line:10%
the gift in the
problem, as they say.

00:19:08.485 --> 00:19:11.110 align:middle line:84%
>> And all we have to do is have
faith that what's been our own

00:19:11.110 --> 00:19:13.180 align:middle line:84%
experience in the
