00:19:13.180 --> 00:19:15.250 align:middle line:84%
continue to be our
experience in the future.

00:19:15.250 --> 00:19:19.390 align:middle line:84%
And then close that gap
between having the experience

00:19:19.390 --> 00:19:21.820 align:middle line:84%
and seeing it for what it
is, rather than seeing it

00:19:21.820 --> 00:19:24.910 align:middle line:84%
five years later as a gift
or three days later as a gift

00:19:24.910 --> 00:19:28.180 align:middle line:84%
or three hours later as a gift
