00:19:28.180 --> 00:19:31.100 align:middle line:84%
and see it as a gift
even as it is occurring.

00:19:31.100 --> 00:19:33.190 align:middle line:90%
That's mastery in living.

00:19:33.190 --> 00:19:35.530 align:middle line:84%
