00:19:38.680 --> 00:19:41.242 align:middle line:84%
What you had said was
interpret it yourself.

00:19:41.242 --> 00:19:42.700 align:middle line:84%
And that's what
you're saying here.

00:19:42.700 --> 00:19:43.870 align:middle line:90%
Decide what it means.

00:19:43.870 --> 00:19:45.520 align:middle line:84%
So it isn't like,
wow, I wonder what

00:19:45.520 --> 00:19:46.880 align:middle line:90%
the universe meant by that.

00:19:46.880 --> 00:19:47.440 align:middle line:90%
What's going on?

00:19:47.440 --> 00:19:47.800 align:middle line:90%
>> That's right.

00:19:47.800 --> 00:19:49.425 align:middle line:84%
The universe hasn't
any secret meaning,

00:19:49.425 --> 00:19:51.383 align:middle line:84%
and the universe does
not have a secret agenda.

00:19:51.383 --> 00:19:53.860 align:middle line:84%
If God had one of those, he
would just tell us what it is.

00:19:53.860 --> 00:19:55.480 align:middle line:84%
