life is that we

00:19:55.480 --> 00:19:58.780 align:middle line:84%
get to define things as
we choose to define them,

00:19:58.780 --> 00:20:02.080 align:middle line:84%
and yet every act is an
act of self definition.

00:20:02.080 --> 00:20:04.300 align:middle line:84%
So yes, we have the
full creative power

00:20:04.300 --> 00:20:06.520 align:middle line:84%
to call a thing what
we choose to call it

00:20:06.520 --> 00:20:08.950 align:middle line:84%
and to describe and
experience to ourselves

00:20:08.950 --> 00:20:10.510 align:middle line:84%
in the way we choose
to describe it.

00:20:10.510 --> 00:20:12.400 align:middle line:84%
And therefore,
having the experience

00:20:12.400 --> 00:20:15.250 align:middle line:84%
itself in a different way,
the moment you describe

00:20:15.250 --> 00:20:17.290 align:middle line:84%
an experience in
a particular way,

00:20:17.290 --> 00:20:19.665 align:middle line:84%
you change the
experience itself.

00:20:19.665 --> 00:20:21.040 align:middle line:84%
It moves right
along with the law

00:20:21.040 --> 00:20:24.280 align:middle line:84%
of physics, which says that
nothing which is observed

00:20:24.280 --> 00:20:27.767 align:middle line:90%
is unaffected by the observer.

00:20:27.767 --> 00:20:30.100 align:middle line:84%
>> I sometimes think of it
as raise it to a higher level

00:20:30.100 --> 00:20:31.870 align:middle line:84%
and try to look at
what's going on there.

00:20:31.870 --> 00:20:34.203 align:middle line:84%
That's another way that we've
been taught, that we can--

00:20:34.203 --> 00:20:35.620 align:middle line:84%
>> That's a beautiful
observation.

00:20:35.620 --> 00:20:37.810 align:middle line:84%
>> Yeah, that we can look
at this life a little bit

00:20:37.810 --> 00:20:38.680 align:middle line:90%
differently.

00:20:38.680 --> 00:20:39.700 align:middle line:90%
But if we realize--

00:20:39.700 --> 00:20:42.760 align:middle line:84%
and I think that's the gift
of the book-- is that these 10

00:20:42.760 --> 00:20:46.375 align:middle line:84%
