thing in our lives.

00:21:14.867 --> 00:21:16.950 align:middle line:84%
>> So we're not going to
get rid of the illusions?

00:21:16.950 --> 00:21:17.750 align:middle line:90%
>> No.

00:21:17.750 --> 00:21:19.580 align:middle line:10%
The idea is to stay
with the illusion,

00:21:19.580 --> 00:21:24.130 align:middle line:10%
but to use it as the tool for
which it was actually created.

00:21:24.130 --> 00:21:26.650 align:middle line:84%
And that's all described
in some detail in the book.

00:21:26.650 --> 00:21:27.730 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

